</li><li> The <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Yakuza" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Yakuza">Yakuza</a></em> series spinoff <em>Ry&#363; ga Gotoku Ishin!</em> has a boss fight inside a bathhouse, where <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FullFrontalAssault" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FullFrontalAssault">both combatants are nude</a> and shielded by conveniently-placed steam clouds. Gets a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CallBack" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CallBack">Call-Back</a> and <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LampshadeHanging" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LampshadeHanging">Lampshade Hanging</a> in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Yakuza1" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Yakuza1">Yakuza Kiwami</a></em> when Kiryu and Majima get into an argument over a movie called <em>Passionate Manly Bathhouse Battle</em>: Majima is convinced it's porn but Kiryu insists that it's a perfectly innocent martial arts piece, and that it's not "indecent" thanks to all the steam.
</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/BulletGirlsPhantasia" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/BulletGirlsPhantasia">Bullet Girls Phantasia</a></em> features three different variations: beams of light, white steam, or black scribbles.
</li><li> In <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Persona4" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/Persona4">Persona 4 Golden</a></em>, after <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">saving Marie from the Hollow Forest</span>, the female members of the Investigation Team are bathing in the Amagi Inn's hot springs, all of whom are very obviously naked save for the steam. Taken to literal extremes with Marie, who is very barely covered by any steam.
</li></ul></div>
