<h2 class="bold font-l">Convenient Steam</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After Selene breaks out of her cryogenic chamber, copious amounts of steam are used to cover her as she lies naked on the floor for at least a minute before she gets up to retrieve her gear. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="kar5bl" data-video-descrip="" data-video-title="Absalom assaults Nami" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/kar5bl_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/kar5bl.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/InvisibleJerkass" data-video-tropename="Invisible Jerkass" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Main/CensorSteam,Manga/OnePiece" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/kar5bl.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Absalom assault...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="45u2xx" data-video-descrip="Stiles sees Malia showering in the boy's locker room, but she doesn't mind the intrusion and her modesty is preserved by the steam from the scalding shower." data-video-title="Malia's Steamy Shower" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/45u2xx_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/snapshot_3_2.png" data-video-trope="Main/CensorSteam" data-video-tropename="Censor Steam" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/TeenWolf,Creator/ShelleyHennig,Main/ShowerOfAwkward,Creator/DylanOBrien" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/snapshot_3_2.png">
<p><span class="bold">Malia's Steamy ...</span></p>
</a>
</div>
